### Chat API smoke tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Send Chat Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "chatId": "demo-room",
  "content": "Hello from VS Code REST client",
  "attachments": []
}

### Get Chat Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages/demo-room
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
